description: Build UWP apps that can view, create and edit PDF documents with ease. Our UI Extension provides a fully customizable user interface with built-in tools for text mark-up, drawing, form filling, full-text searching and so much more. Using our Core API your developers can code with our PDF libraries quickly and proficiently, harnessing Foxit’s powerful PDF SDK technology to give your customers a great product. Created with UWP’s fluent design guidelines in mind, our PDF SDK is the perfect companion for any UWP mobile app.
title: Foxit PDF SDK For UWP
